===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*kap-}}{{root|en|ine-pro|*kap-|id1=head}}
From {{inh|en|enm|catel|}}, from {{der|en|xno|catel||personal property}}, from {{der|en|fro-nor|-}} (compare {{cog|fr|cheptel}}, {{cog|fro|chetel}}, {{m|fro|chatel}}, also English {{doublet|en|chattel|notext=1}}) from {{der|en|ML.|capitāle}}, from {{der|en|la|capitālis||of the head}} (whence also {{doublet|en|capital|notext=1}}, from {{m|la|caput||head}} + {{m|la|-alis||-al}}). For the sense evolution, compare {{l|en|pecuniary}} and {{l|en|fee}}. Also compare {{m+|ru|поголо́вье||total number of livestock}} from {{m+|ru|голова́||head}}. {{doublet|en|capital|chattel}}.

