===Noun===
{{en-noun|p|sg=cattle}}

# {{senseid|en|Q830}}[[domesticated|Domesticated]] animal of the species {{taxfmt|Bos taurus|species}} ([[cow]]s, [[bull]]s, [[steer]]s, [[ox]]en etc), and other [[hoof]]ed mammals of the genus {{taxfmt|Bos|genus}}.
#: {{ux|en|Many '''cattle''' were suffering from a disease called [[BSE]].}}
# Certain other [[livestock]], such as [[sheep]], [[pig]]s or [[goat]]s. Also rarely applied to [[horse]]s.
